      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"southern edge\"? I was specifically talking about the northern edge. If your sensors are saying the northern edge is fine but my tape measure is showing a 2-inch shift, we have a serious discrepancy. If I report this as a deviation from the approved blueprints, I'll have to issue a formal Work Stop order until a full audit is done. Are you sure you aren't misrepresenting the data here? I need a definitive answer on the northern edge.",
